headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Walmart vs. Target
summary: Walmart (NYSE: WMT) shareholders are basking in a record-setting year, with strong growth propelling the stock to a fantastic 81% return thus far in 2024, at the time of writing.  In contrast, Target (NYSE: TGT) shareholders have endured a year to forget, with the stock falling 7% year to date.  Can the fantastic rally in Walmart stock continue, or could a potential comeback from Target kick off a big return for its shares going forward?
